review_text: Really nice and quick tutorial, easy to follow. I liked the fact that contained a full deployment and payment sections.

The course covers a lot of topics and the teachers explain them very well. There is a lot of hands on coding if you want but all the code is also provided for review. The big downside is thet the basis for the agents (AutoGen) is an old version (0.2) that is not supported anymore by Microsoft. The current version of AutoGen works very differently so the whle course would need to be remade for that.

Great course and I liked the way it was structured. The only draw back was the initial setup was repeated multiple times and the results of the output from LLMs were read every time in detail, which was a bit time consuming. Other than that, it is a solid course which will give a good understanding and practical implementation of AI Agent implementation.
